<inglise> For the operations referred to under point 1 (a) the Commission will start the procedure for making the payments into the Fund as soon as the Council has formally adopted the basic decision. </inglise>
<eesti> Punktis 1a nimetatud toimingute tegemiseks alustab komisjon maksemenetlust niipea, kui n&otilde;ukogu on ametlikult p&otilde;hiotsuse vastu v&otilde;tnud. </eesti>
<inglise> The amount to be paid into the Fund will be calculated on the basis of the total amount for the operation decided on by the Council. </inglise>
