<inglise> For the operations referred to under point 1 (b), payments into the Fund will be made in annual tranches calculated on the basis of the annual amounts indicated in the financial statement attached to the Commission proposal, adapted where appropriate in the light of the Council decision. </inglise>
<eesti> Punktis 1b nimetatud toimingute tegemiseks tehakse maksed fondi iga-aastaste osadena iga-aastaste summade alusel, mis on n&auml;idatud komisjoni ettepanekule lisatud raamatupidamisaruandes, mida vastavalt olukorrale korrigeeritakse n&otilde;ukogu otsuse valguses. </eesti>
